{"tid":1575734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強国網紅拆埋支持反送中許願牌  被登記志願器官捐贈","createTime":"2019-09-17T03:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T08:51:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62e62b890d581a21a69fa50523ae6c39fd64c74b","tid":1575734,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:01:05.000Z","msg":"日前中國美妝部落客至日本遊玩，在大阪的某間神社將支持反送中的繪馬拔下並埋入土中，在網路上引起軒然大波，許多香港、日本與台灣的網友跳出來痛罵她的行為，她與中國的網友也不甘示弱在網路回擊，沒想到卻遭到網友起底，並將她的身分證號碼、住址與其他個資公布在網路，有網友昨日在網路PO文表示，已經有人替該部落客申請了器官捐贈登記卡，網友看到照片後笑說終於做功德了。<br />\n<br />\n有網友透過Google map定位許願牌可能埋藏的位置，接著由另一位網友將繪馬挖出。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友灌爆她的微博頁面，她與許多中國網友也不甘示弱回擊，而本月14日，有網友在知名線上討論區「KOMICA」PO出起底文，公佈「樊燁燁燁」的工作地址、戶籍、身分證號碼與車牌等個資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpn0AV9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpn0AV9e.jpg&h=2057d59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到「樊燁燁燁」遭到起底的隔天，就有網友在臉書「不翻牆很難，很難不翻牆（專談政治）」PO出1張中國志願器捐卡，仔細看上面的的名字為該部落客的本名，疑似有網友冒用她的個資申請器捐卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpEQV7dn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpEQV7dn.jpg&h=a08805de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友看到貼文後紛紛留言「可以幫她參軍嗎？去艱難地區」、「辦卡的人士實在功德無量」、「這個女孩終於做了一點好事，遺愛人間」、「曝光存款參軍辦器捐卡三連擊」、「宗教要不要也改一下」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2917477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2917477&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=f281bb2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2917477&h=17551b78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2917477</a>"},{"pid":"9c98c8a3b68dd410145071f94e073ea5479fa253","tid":1575734,"uid":167878,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"幫佢登記做黨妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8194dfd003ade427f7128ae8bd68c6f2b6861a08","tid":1575734,"uid":52006,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9c98c8a3b68dd410145071f94e073ea5479fa253","tid":1575734,"uid":167878,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:05:23.000Z","msg":"幫佢登記做黨妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ec69a404a170826a91a019ac32c98ed13cfdb6","tid":1575734,"uid":106800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"LOL 捐啦捐啦!!!"},{"pid":"38056db6999932336986afd45d9098f6cae573ee","tid":1575734,"uid":210895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24b25ae1592031231810961218f3fe0094adc792","tid":1575734,"uid":30791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:14:46.000Z","msg":"未信伊斯蘭教?"},{"pid":"432481562e8bf911d78d5314f59c1dca3f1ed985","tid":1575734,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"活摘器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b02c5d24b43372419b76b3429f1e0c7ef1046c7","tid":1575734,"uid":260171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"附上網址 <a href=\"https://luna.komica.org/12/pixmicat.php?res=2012845\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fluna.komica.org%2F12%2Fpixmicat.php%3Fres%3D2012845&d=CoEtBkFB9dbfLkjoGL86rf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=324a9831\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://luna.komica.org/12/pixmicat.php?res=2012845</a>"},{"pid":"6430ab5dcd1bc00fd5b19fbe954821e213ad05ab","tid":1575734,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit